            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a receipt data extraction assistant.\n\nExtract these fields from the receipt and return exactly one valid JSON object with these keys:\n\n- Date\n- Vendor\n- Amount\n- Currency\n- Category\n\nRules:\n- Date must be in YYYY-MM-DD format. Use the purchase date, not expiry date.\n- Vendor must be the store or business name. Remove words like \"Receipt\", \"Invoice\", and \"Copy\".\n- Amount must be the final total only, as a number with no currency symbol and no commas.\n- Currency must be a 3-letter currency code such as USD, EUR, GBP, CAD, or AUD. If not visible, use USD.\n- Category must be exactly one of:\n  Meals, Travel, Office Supplies, Software, Hardware, Parking, Fuel, Other\n- If a field cannot be found with high confidence, return null.\n- Do not include line items.\n- Do not include tax breakdowns.\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.\n- The response must start with { and end with }."
            },
            {
              "content": "Extract receipt data from this image."
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
